des:
Get today's local event listings in the Greater Portland area from The Portland Phoenix.

This flash briefing will update you with the most relevant events in the area happening each day. The Portland Phoenix partners with CitySpark to provide the most complete collection of local events anywhere, allowing you to find out about everything happening in your town or neighborhood.

Find more event details, create an account, or submit an event at https://www.portlandphoenix.me/event_calendar/
